article_title: Dozens killed in Israeli air strike on northern Gaza, Hamas-run authorities say.
sentence: Dozens  killed  in  Israeli  air  strike  on  northern  Gaza,  Hamas-run  authorities  say.

article_title: Dozens killed in Israeli air strike on northern Gaza, Hamas-run authorities say.
sentence: At  least  33  people  have  been  killed  and  85  others  wounded  in  Israeli  air  strikes  at  Jabalia  refugee  camp  in  northern  Gaza  on  Friday,  the  strip's  Hamas-run  authorities  say.
